First Half Density: 4% keyword density

Calculate: (Total word count ÷ 2) × 0.04 = required keyword mentions in first half
Example: 1,600 words ÷ 2 = 800 words × 0.04 = 32 keyword mentions needed


Second Half Density: 2% keyword density

Calculate: (Total word count ÷ 2) × 0.02 = required keyword mentions in second half
Example: 1,600 words ÷ 2 = 800 words × 0.02 = 16 keyword mentions needed


